 surface and unprecedentedly detailed characterization, Betelgeuse\nopens a window to episodic surface mass ejection in the late-stage evolution of\nmassive stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 May 2023 18:06:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-18"}
