iscussion\n  New methodological approaches are required for more efficient analysis of the\nincreasing amount of high-dimensional data collected in randomised clinical\ntrials. We highlight the limitations and barriers to the current use of\nhigh-dimensional data in trials, and suggest potential avenues for improvement\nand future work.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 May 2023 12:59:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-18"}
