ases. The latter results are preliminary because the poorly known\nsolubilities and activities of volatile elements in silicate melts must be\nconsidered for the correct equilibrium distribution, condensation temperatures\nand mass balance of F, Cl, Br, I, H, S, Se and Te bearing species between melt\nand vapor (abridged).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 May 2023 23:06:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-24"}
